The FileOps class defines the operation and behavior of the entire backup process.

Constructor that takes a FileSet to conduct operations with and a FileOpsMessageHandler that will take call-backs with Progress updates as the operation progresses.

Constructor that takes a FileSet to conduct operations on.
FileOpsMessageHandler - Interface in core
Defines required methods for any class that wants to receive Progress updates from the FileOps operation as it proceeds.
